# teaser: Create an SEO friendly and user friendly URL structure and navigation for a new website
- id: 2996-structure-strategy
  title: Structure Strategy
  tags:
  - web-development
  - structure
  - strategy
  family: Web Development
  body: Your task is to create a detailed URL and navigation structure for a complete
    website using the [PROMPT] and the [KEYWORD] and [BUSINESS TYPE] and [EXISTING
    URL] in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. The sections and categories should be organized hierarchically,
    with the Home page at the top and the more specific pages at the bottom. If there
    is an existing URL use that URL for the main and sub urls. Write a summary for
    each section explaining the purpose of the section. Use your knowledge of how
    to make the best structure in terms of linking and SEO to get to the top positions
    in Google. Use your knowledge of what search users want to create a helpful informative
    website. All output should be in English.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - keyword
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
